{"tid":655172,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多人轉左用無矽洗頭水？","createTime":"2018-05-06T09:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T22:37:16.000Z","uid":33568,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e020eb28053023f06d6d4ba3ccbf1aa6117496db","tid":655172,"uid":33568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:43:23.000Z","msg":"以前用普通洗頭水<br />\n頭皮會好痕好紅 有時會好似洗唔乾淨咁一舊野<br />\n後尾上網睇先知矽呢樣野<br />\n就轉左用無矽洗頭水<br />\n果陣都冇乜牌子出無矽 用左好耐啲好乾既洗頭水<br />\n但頭皮問題完全冇曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到依家好多牌子出無矽真係好開心<br />\n同埋平左好多 質素又好 好多用完都勁滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推薦大家一齊用無矽 仲可以減少脫髮問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb2fbb2894d1f9eb0f6730471a35da1a0ab8c93","tid":655172,"uid":151664,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:47:25.000Z","msg":"想脫髮應該用邊隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  頭髮厚到仆街"},{"pid":"834dd7fbe1732f131c2fc5feb4b1fb683df82bcc","tid":655172,"uid":163954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"abb2fbb2894d1f9eb0f6730471a35da1a0ab8c93","tid":655172,"uid":151664,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:47:25.000Z","msg":"想脫髮應該用邊隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  頭髮厚到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"過多一兩年就自然會變薄，到時可能連洗頭水都唔駛用"},{"pid":"202f8b09c55bbcd60c4360f83f1d9a442f0ca008","tid":655172,"uid":33568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abb2fbb2894d1f9eb0f6730471a35da1a0ab8c93","tid":655172,"uid":151664,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:47:25.000Z","msg":"想脫髮應該用邊隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  頭髮厚到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"每日紮頭髮 cool到實 有都變冇"},{"pid":"6133b3e91442d267285ec51d9715f288cdd5a8fc","tid":655172,"uid":151664,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":